    Inspired by the years we spent crafting our technique and conditioning our bodies in ballet class, The Body Conditioning Balm delivers performance like no other moisturiser on the market. INGREDIENT BENEFITS

+
-

Our formulations are like a professional performer: meticulously crafted and endlessly rehearsed to be "show-ready." After nearly 2 years of development (or 16 if you count our years in ballet class), we've perfected this innovative product just for you. With countless modifications, we've ensured our quality ingredients work seamlessly together to elevate your morning routine and deliver "show-stopping" performance beyond just moisturising.

  • KEY INGREDIENTS

    • GATULINE IN-TENSE MB: Clinically proven to help boost collagen production within the deep layers of the skin, visibly firming and smoothing skin.

    SHEA BUTTER: Intensely moisturises, leaving skin soft and supple with long-lasting hydration.

    COCOA BUTTER: Deeply nourishes and improves skin elasticity for a youthful appearance.

    LACTIC ACID: Exfoliates gently, promoting cell turnover for brighter, more even-toned skin.

    APRICOT KERNEL OIL: Rejuvenates and revitalises, enhancing skin’s natural radiance.

    ALOE VERA: Soothes and cools, providing relief from irritation and inflammation.

    OLIVE SQUALANE: Mimics skin’s natural oils, ensuring optimal hydration and smoothness.

    VITAMIN E: Shields skin from oxidative stress, maintaining a youthful, healthy glow.

    CALENDULA OIL: Promotes healing and reduces sensitivity, perfect for delicate skin.
